{"tid":1660353,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【連登之殤】霖霖之死！","createTime":"2019-10-17T12:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T13:24:58.000Z","uid":167548,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1837d9b90b53efd9ae72dd0d9aaa7e47284b28ea","tid":1660353,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:44:01.000Z","msg":"你地幾時先肯好似8.18遊行咁樣出盡力去宣傳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地繼續做偵探啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />霖霖將永遠得唔到公義<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n其實呢 就霖霖100%他殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後死黑警睇完片就改自殺, 唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位大偵探你地查HKDI CCTV沒咩用,<br />\n真正有用是附近街道CCTV根本就拎唔到</blockquote><br />\n真是好好笑, 明明就是HKDI之後失去蹤跡, 你地咬死HKDI有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如前幾日啊Black巴打所言屬實, 亦即是去完地鐵站之後出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n還原真相所需要o既CCTV唔單止是HKDI, 更要附近街道+黨鐵交CCTV配合<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果呢場仗輸左, 霖霖永遠沉冤枉死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果呢場仗贏左, 霖霖先可能沉冤得雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你問我想點？<br />\n一個字,<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">It is Victory, Victory at all costs</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NCtQL5MOcZ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNCtQL5MOcZ0&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAfkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=46fbe979\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NCtQL5MOcZ0</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">攬炒巴9.29「全球連線 共抗極權」行動預告</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">2:15</span><br />\n內有中文解釋, 方便街外人去睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/spj3NoG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fspj3NoG.jpg&h=2a584524&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">為左所有逝去嘅手足霖霖, 仍至所有香港人！<br />\n除了血液，辛勞，眼淚和汗水，我什麼也沒提供！<br />\n這是勝利，不惜一切代價的勝利！<br />\n儘管取得了所有的恐怖，還是取得了勝利-勝利，無論道路多麼艱辛，因為沒有勝利就無法生存！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1c25aa298584fe18ba8601a9d04dde016e6b4132","tid":1660353,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:44:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHn4YGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHn4YGm.jpg&h=a9bf801a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3e3aa553f3243c91dbe932d7ae1485b15c37e07e","tid":1660353,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:48:11.000Z","msg":"真是唔知你地想點？"},{"pid":"354e6fb2429ac3647518e8d0650a936735b383fe","tid":1660353,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:49:04.000Z","msg":"現實就是曬你地時間, 玩謝連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4a0aba0d35bf6488780e0d9c11a832fd46f172","tid":1660353,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:51:13.000Z","msg":"根本霖霖件事只需要直接指責黑警查案不力, <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全裸浮屍講成自殺</span></span></strong>就是最有力o既argument<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c00bc9613139ccfddff9b0868098c252f7b007","tid":1660353,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xfSkPF4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxfSkPF4.jpg&h=0f9524ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc515b1d2f96a3ac9369080bfb83acd4534c7779","tid":1660353,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:57